                     <interp inst="t17600521-25-person288" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am constable; I was sent for about 6 o'clock to the prosecutor's house; the prisoner was delivered into my charge with the keys.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence.</p>
               <p>I found them keys in a house in Golden-lane, which had been a smith's shop.</p>
